title: Wednesday Post Show (09-22-21)
itunes:title: Wednesday Post Show (09-22-21)
description:
A caller defends Lunchbox saying that he had the right to take the couch off the side of the road without paying anything for it. Amy also says that Lunchbox double dipped money in Vegas. We dive into Lunchbox’s obsession with money and why we think he doesn’t put ‘good money energy’ into the universe. We play another round of 20 questions to see if they can guess the famous person. It gets heated.
